{"tid":2374575,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"C.朗與皇馬主席冰釋前嫌！他對皇馬仍有感情","createTime":"2021-01-21T10:27:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-21T14:22:56.000Z","uid":147522,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2b4efb745f95ad388dcd8427afe002073ea1983e","tid":2374575,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T10:27:53.000Z","msg":"　　C.朗拿度（Cristiano Ronaldo）和皇馬主席佩雷斯（Florentino Perez）的關係已經徹底修復，C.朗拿度如今依然能感受到和皇馬的親密感。<br />\n<br />\n　　《馬卡報》披露，本週佩雷斯造訪了祖雲達斯訓練基地，和C.朗拿度見了面，看起來兩人早已冰釋前嫌。2018年，C.朗拿度離開皇馬轉投祖雲達斯，當時他和皇馬主席的關係完全破裂了，不過從去年三月起，關係開始修復，C.朗拿度一度出現在班拿貝的看台上觀看比賽。<br />\n<br />\n　　《馬卡報》稱，如今C.朗拿度仍然感受到與皇馬的特殊橋樑，在班拿貝的九年時光里，他成為了球會的傳奇，438場攻入450球，並且拿到過4次歐聯和2次西甲冠軍，他個人的金球獎中，有4次是作為皇馬球員拿到的。"},{"pid":"902c1885a4acbd72ec2f38c139ee18cfb3b05a76","tid":2374575,"uid":52571,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T10:30:48.000Z","msg":"佩雷斯接受了C.朗的誠懇道歉。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6546b20796f20f1c5aae9c4b249906cd8fd80aee","tid":2374575,"uid":307927,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T10:37:26.000Z","msg":"返皇馬啦 大家都需要大家"},{"pid":"632d6bf8124ecb13c1847f73fbcaa10c554480cc","tid":2374575,"uid":76310,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6546b20796f20f1c5aae9c4b249906cd8fd80aee","tid":2374575,"uid":307927,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T10:37:26.000Z","msg":"返皇馬啦 大家都需要大家"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T10:45:55.000Z","msg":"who needs c ron?"},{"pid":"73b1eb0ecb7a7ed95ac17a91f293838d1a629a71","tid":2374575,"uid":307927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"632d6bf8124ecb13c1847f73fbcaa10c554480cc","tid":2374575,"uid":76310,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6546b20796f20f1c5aae9c4b249906cd8fd80aee","tid":2374575,"uid":307927,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T10:37:26.000Z","msg":"返皇馬啦 大家都需要大家"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T10:45:55.000Z","msg":"who needs